# Syntax documentation

The `.jianpu` input syntax is documented in `syntax.md`.

When you change user-facing syntax behavior in `src/parser/` or `src/desugar.rs`:

1. Update `syntax.md` in the same commit to describe the new or changed syntax.
2. Stage `syntax.md` together with the syntax code changes.
